EUR-chT (Men) 2nd (1961), Oberhausen FRG, rd 1, Jun-21 
English Opening: King's English Variation. Reversed Sicilian (A21)

1. c4 e5 2. Nc3 d6 3. g3 f5 4. d4 e4 5. f3 Nf6 6. Bg2 ef3 7. Nf3 g6 8. O-O Bg7 9. e4 fe4 10. Ng5 O-O 11. Nge4 Ne4 12. Rf8 Qf8 13. Ne4 Nc6 14. Be3 Bf5 15. Qd2 Re8 16. Ng5 Re3 17. Bd5 Kh8 18. Nf7 Qf7 Tal isn't interested in a draw. 19. Bf7 Rd3 20. Qe2 Bd4 21. Kg2 Ne5 22. Rd1 Re3 23. Qf1 Be4 24. Kh3 Rf3 25. Qe2 Bf5
